casebody.data:
Deloris Grace YOUNG, BY AND THROUGH her attorney-in-fact Robert A. YOUNG and Joan E. Ambrose, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
RALLY APPRAISAL, L.L.C. and Fuhrmeister Appraisal, L.L.C., Defendants-Appellees. No. 18-0942 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 3, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A beneficiary of an estate challenges the grant of summary judgment to two appraisal companies on her claim of negligent misrepresentation. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
